  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/2026`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `औद्योगिक विकास बैंक (उपक्रम का अंतरण और निरसन) अधिनियम,2003`
  actYear (2003)
  ministry `Ministry of Finance`
  department `Department of Financial Services`
  longTitle `An Act to provide for the transfer and vesting of the undertaking of the Industrial Development Bank of India to, and in, the Company to be formed and registered as a Company under the Companies Act, 1956 to carry on banking business and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto and also to repeal the Industrial Development Bank of India Act, 1964.`
