obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (32326)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title and commencement.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes `1. 2nd July, 2004, vide notification No. S.O. 769(E) dated 2nd July, 2004, see Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(ii).`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32326&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the Industrial Development Bank`
  line `(Transfer of Undertaking and Repeal) Act, 2003.`
  line
  line `(2) It shall come into force on such date ^1`
  line `as the Central Government may, by notification, appoint.`
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (32327)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title Definitions.
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32327&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires,--`
  line
  line `(a) "appointed day" means such date as the Central Government may, by notification, appoint`
  line `under section 3;`
  line
  line `(b) "Company" means the Industrial Development Bank of India Limited to be formed and`
  line `registered under the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956);`
  line
  line `(c) "Development Bank" means the Industrial Development Bank of India established under`
  line `sub-section (1) of section 3 of the Industrial Development Bank of India Act, 1964 (18 of 1964);`
  line
  line `(d) "notification" means a notification published in the Official Gazette;`
  line
  line `(e) "Reserve Bank" means the Reserve Bank of India constituted under the Reserve Bank of India`
  line `Act, 1934 (2 of 1934).`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (32328)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Undertaking of Development Bank to vest in Company.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32328&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `(1) On such date as the Central`
  line `Government may, by notification, appoint, there shall be transferred to, and vest in, the Company, the`
  line `undertaking of Development Bank.`
  line
  line `(2) Notwithstanding anything contained in the Banking Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949), the`
  line `Company referred to in sub-section (1) shall be deemed to be a banking company within the meaning of`
  line `clause (c) of section 5 of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949 and as such shall carry on banking business in`
  line `accordance with the provisions of that Act, ^1***:`
  line
  line `Provided that such Company shall not be required to--`
  line
  line `(a) obtain licence under section 22 of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949);`
  line
  line `(b) maintain for a period of five years from the appointed day the percentage of assets required to`
  line `be maintained under section 24 of the said Act.`
  line
  line `^2[Provided further that the provisions of clause (a) to the proviso, shall cease to be applicable`
  line `immediately after the commencement of Part XIII of the Finance Act, 2021 (13 of 2021), and from such commencement, the Company shall be deemed to have obtained licence under section 22 of the`
  line `Banking Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949).]`
  line
  line `(3) The provisions of the Banking Regulation Act, 1949 (10 of 1949) shall, as far as may be, to the`
  line `extent they are not repugnant to any provision of this Act, apply to such Company.`
  line
  line `(4) Notwithstanding anything contained in the Banking Regulation Act,1949 (10 of 1949), the Central`
  line `Government may, in consultation with the Reserve Bank of India, by notification, direct that any of the`
  line `provisions of that Act specified in the notification--`
  line
  line `(a) shall not apply to the Company; or`
  line
  line `(b) shall apply to the Company, only with such exceptions, modifications and the adaptations as`
  line `may be specified in the notification.`
  line
  line `(5) A copy of every notification proposed to be issued under sub-section (4), shall be laid in draft`
  line `before each House of Parliament, while it is in session, for a total period of thirty days which may be`
  line `comprised in one session or in two or more successive sessions, and if, before the expiry of the session`
  line `immediately following the session or the successive sessions aforesaid, both Houses agree in`
  line `disapproving the issue of the notification or both Houses agree in making any modification in the`
  line `notification, the notification shall not be issued or, as the case may be, shall be issued only in such`
  line `modified form as may be agreed upon by both the Houses.`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line `1. The words in addition to the business which may be carried on and transacted by the Development Bank omitted by Act 13 of 2021, s. 165 (w.e.f. 01-04-2021).`
  line
  line `2. The proviso ins by s. 165, ibid. (w.e.f. 01-04-2021).`
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (32329)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `General effect of transfer and vesting of undertaking.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32329&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `(1) The Central Government, being the`
  line `shareholder of the Development Bank and every other shareholder of the Development Bank immediately`
  line `before the appointed day shall be deemed to be registered on and from the appointed day as a shareholder`
  line `of the Company to the extent of the face value of the shares held by such shareholder.`
  line
  line `(2) The undertaking of the Development Bank which is transferred to, and which vest in, the`
  line `Company under section 3 shall be deemed to include all business, assets, rights, powers, authorities and`
  line `privileges and all properties, movable and immovable, real and personal, corporeal and incorporeal, in`
  line `possession or reservation, present or contingent of whatever nature and wheresoever situate including`
  line `lands, buildings, vehicles, cash balances, deposits, foreign currencies, disclosed and undisclosed reserves,`
  line `reserve fund, special reserve fund, benevolent reserve fund, any other fund, stocks, investments, shares,`
  line `bonds, debentures, security, management of any industrial concern, loans, advances and guarantees given`
  line `to any person or industrial concern, tenancies, leases and book debts and all other rights and interests`
  line `arising out of such property as were immediately before the appointed day in the ownership, possession or`
  line `power of the Development Bank in relation to its undertaking, within or without India, all books of`
  line `account, registers, records and documents relating thereto and shall also be deemed to include all`
  line `borrowings, liabilities and obligations of whatever kind within or without India then subsisting of the`
  line `Development Bank in relation to its respective undertaking.`
  line
  line `(3) All contracts, deeds, bonds, guarantees, powers of attorney, other instruments and working`
  line `arrangements subsisting immediately before the appointed day and affecting the Development Bank shall`
  line `cease to have effect or to be enforceable against the Development Bank and shall be of as full force and`
  line `effect against or in favour of the Company in which the undertaking of the Development Bank has vested`
  line `by virtue of this Act and enforceable as fully and effectually as if instead of the Development Bank, the`
  line `Company had been named therein or had been a party thereto.`
  line
  line `(4) Any proceeding or cause of action pending or existing immediately before the appointed day by or`
  line `against the Development Bank in relation to its undertaking may, as from the appointed day, be continued`
  line `and enforced by or against the Company in which the undertaking of the Development Bank has vested`
  line `by virtue of this Act as it might have been enforced by or against the Development Bank if this Act had`
  line `not been enacted and shall cease to be enforceable by or against the Development Bank.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  sectionId (32330)
  sectionNo (5)
  orderNo 5
  title `Provisions in respect of officers and other employees of Development Bank.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_5_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32330&sectionno=5&orderno=5&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line `(1) Every officer`
  line `or other employee of the Development Bank (except a director of the Board or the chairman and`
  line `managing director or any whole-time director) serving in the employment immediately before the`
  line `appointed day shall, in so far as such officer or other employee is employed in connection with the`
  line `undertaking which has vested in the Company by virtue of this Act, become, as from the appointed day,`
  line `an officer or, as the case may be, other employee of the Company and shall hold his office or service`
  line `therein by the same tenure, at the same remuneration, upon the same terms and conditions, with the same`
  line `obligations and with the same rights and privileges as to leave, leave fare concession, welfare scheme,`
  line `medical benefit scheme, insurance, provident fund, other funds, retirement, voluntary retirement, gratuity`
  line `and other benefits as he would have held under the Development Bank if its undertaking had not vested in`
  line `the Company and shall continue to do so as an officer or, as the case may be, other employee of the`
  line `Company or until the expiry of a period of six months from the appointed day, if such officer or other`
  line `employee opts not to continue to be the officer or other employee of the Company within such period.`
  line
  line `(2) Where an officer or other employee of the Development Bank opts under sub-section (1) not to be`
  line `in employment or service of the company, such officer or other employee shall be deemed to have`
  line resigned.
  line
  line `(3) Notwithstanding anything contained in the Industrial Disputes Act, 1947 (14 of 1947), or in any`
  line `other law for the time being in force, the transfer of the services of any officer or other employee of the`
  line `Development Bank to the Company shall not entitle such officer or other employee to any compensation`
  line `under this Act or under any other law for the time being in force and no such claim shall be entertained by`
  line `any court, tribunal or other authority.`
  line
  line `(4) The officers and other employees who have retired before the appointed day from the service of`
  line `the Development Bank and are entitled to any benefits, rights or privileges shall be entitled to receive the`
  line `same benefits, rights or privileges from the Company.`
  line
  line `(5) The trust of the provident fund or the gratuity fund of the Development Bank and any other bodies`
  line `created for the welfare of officers or employees would continue to discharge their functions in the`
  line `Company as was being done hitherto in the Development Bank and any tax exemption granted to the`
  line `provident fund or the gratuity fund or pension fund would continue to be applied to the Company.`
  line
  line `(6) Notwithstanding anything contained in this Act or in the Companies Act, 1956 (1 of 1956), or in`
  line `any other law for the time being in force or in the regulations of the Development Bank, no director of the`
  line `Board, chairman and managing director or any whole-time director or any other person entitled to manage`
  line `the whole or substantial part of the business and affairs of the Development Bank shall be entitled to any`
  line `compensation against the Development Bank or the Company for the loss of office or for the premature`
  line `termination of any contract of management entered into by him with the Development Bank.`
obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_6:
  sectionId (32331)
  sectionNo (6)
  orderNo 6
  title `Concession, etc., to be deemed to have been granted to Company.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_6_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32331&sectionno=6&orderno=6&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_6_content:
  string
  line `With effect from the`
  line `appointed day, all fiscal and other concessions, licences, benefits, privileges and exemptions granted to`
  line `the Development Bank, in connection with the affairs and business of the Development Bank under any`
  line `law for the time being in force shall be deemed to have been granted to the Company.`
obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_7:
  sectionId (32332)
  sectionNo (7)
  orderNo 7
  title `Tax exemption or benefit to continue to have effect.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_7_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_7_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32332&sectionno=7&orderno=7&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_7_content:
  string
  line `(1) Where any exemption from, or any`
  line `assessment with respect to, any tax has been granted or made or any benefit by way of set off or carry`
  line `forward of any unabsorbed depreciation or investment allowance or other allowance or loss has been`
  line `extended or is available to the Development Bank under the Income-tax Act, 1961 (43 of 1961), such`
  line `exemption, assessment or benefit shall continue to have effect in relation to the Company.`
  line
  line `(2) Where any payment made by the Development Bank is exempted from deduction of tax at source`
  line `under any provision of the Income-tax Act,1961 (43 of 1961), such exemption will continue to be`
  line `available as if the provisions of the said Act made applicable to the Development Bank were operative in`
  line `relation to the Company.`
  line
  line `(3) The transfer and vesting of the undertaking of the Development Bank or any part thereof in terms`
  line `of section 3 shall not be construed as a transfer within the meaning of the Income-tax Act, 1961`
  line `(43 of 1961) or any other law for the time being in force.`
obj_root_law_sections_7_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_8:
  sectionId (32333)
  sectionNo (8)
  orderNo 8
  title `Guarantee to be operative.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_8_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_8_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32333&sectionno=8&orderno=8&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_8_content:
  string
  line `Any guarantee given for or in favour of the Development Bank with`
  line `respect to any loan, lease, finance or other assistance shall continue to be operative in relation to the`
  line Company.
obj_root_law_sections_8_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_9:
  sectionId (32334)
  sectionNo (9)
  orderNo 9
  title `Shares, bonds and debentures to be deemed to be approved securities.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_9_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_9_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32334&sectionno=9&orderno=9&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_9_content:
  string
  line Notwithstanding
  line `anything contained in any other law for the time being in force, the shares, bonds and debentures of the`
  line `Company shall be deemed to be approved securities for the purposes of the Indian Trusts Act, 1882`
  line `(2 of 1882) and the Insurance Act, 1938 (4 of1938).`
obj_root_law_sections_9_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_10:
  sectionId (32335)
  sectionNo (10)
  orderNo 10
  title `Act to have overriding effect.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_10_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_10_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32335&sectionno=10&orderno=10&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_10_content:
  string
  line `The provisions of this Act shall have effect notwithstanding`
  line `anything inconsistent therewith contained in any enactment other than this Act or in any instrument`
  line `having effect by virtue of any enactment other than this Act.`
obj_root_law_sections_10_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_11:
  sectionId (32336)
  sectionNo (11)
  orderNo 11
  title `Application of other laws not barred.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_11_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_11_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32336&sectionno=11&orderno=11&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_11_content:
  string
  line `The provisions of this Act shall be in addition to, and`
  line `not in derogation of the provisions of any other law for the time being in force.`
obj_root_law_sections_11_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_12:
  sectionId (32337)
  sectionNo (12)
  orderNo 12
  title `Amendment to certain enactments.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_12_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_12_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32337&sectionno=12&orderno=12&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_12_content:
  string
  line `The enactments specified in the Schedule to this Act shall`
  line `be amended in the manner provided therein.`
obj_root_law_sections_12_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_13:
  sectionId (32338)
  sectionNo (13)
  orderNo 13
  title `Substitution in Acts, rules, regulations or notifications by Company in place of Development Bank.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_13_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_13_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32338&sectionno=13&orderno=13&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_13_content:
  string
  line `In every Act, rule, regulation or notification in force on the appointed day,`
  line
  line `(a) for the words Industrial Development Bank of India, wherever they occur, the words`
  line `Industrial Development Bank of India Limited referred to in clause (b) of section 2 of the Industrial`
  line `Development Bank (Transfer of Undertaking and Repeal) Act, 2003 shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(b) for the words Development Bank, wherever they occur, the words Industrial Development`
  line `Bank of India Limited referred to in clause (b) of section 2 of the Industrial Development Bank`
  line `(Transfer of Undertaking and Repeal) Act, 2003 shall be substituted;`
  line
  line `(c) for the words and figures the Development Bank means the Industrial Development Bank of`
  line `India, established under section 3 of the Industrial Development Bank of India Act, 1964 (18 of`
  line `1964), the words, brackets, letter and figures the Industrial Development Bank of India Limited`
  line `referred to in clause (b) of section 2 of the Industrial Development Bank (Transfer of Undertaking`
  line `and Repeal) Act, 2003 shall be substituted.`
  line
  line `(d) for the words and figures the Industrial Development Bank of India, established under`
  line `section 3 of the Industrial Development Bank of India Act, 1964 (18 of 1964), the words, brackets,`
  line `letter and figures the Industrial Development Bank of India Limited referred to in clause (b) of`
  line `section 2 of the Industrial Development Bank (Transfer of Undertaking and Repeal) Act, 2003 shall`
  line `be substituted.`
obj_root_law_sections_13_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_14:
  sectionId (32339)
  sectionNo (14)
  orderNo 14
  title `Power to remove difficulties.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_14_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_14_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32339&sectionno=14&orderno=14&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_14_content:
  string
  line `(1) If any difficulty arises in giving effect to the provisions of`
  line `this Act, the Central Government may, by order published in the Official Gazette, make such provisions`
  line `not inconsistent with the provisions of this Act as may appear to it to be necessary or expedient for`
  line `removing the difficulty:`
  line
  line `Provided that no such order shall be made after the expiry of three years from the date of`
  line `commencement of this Act.`
  line
  line `(2) Every order made under this section shall be laid, as soon as maybe after it is made, before each`
  line `House of Parliament.`
obj_root_law_sections_14_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_15:
  sectionId (32340)
  sectionNo (15)
  orderNo 15
  title `Repeal and saving of Act 18 of 1964.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_15_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_15_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053&sectionId=32340&sectionno=15&orderno=15&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_11_00048_200353_1517807326053
obj_root_law_sections_15_content:
  string
  line `(1) On the appointed day, the Industrial Development`
  line `Bank of India Act, 1964, shall stand repealed.`
  line
  line `(2) Notwithstanding the repeal of the Industrial Development Bank of India Act, 1964, the provisions`
  line `of section 30A of the Act so repealed will continue to be applicable in respect of the arrangement entered`
  line `into by the Development Bank with an industrial concern up to the appointed day and the Company will`
  line `be entitled to act upon and enforce the same as fully and effectually as if this Act has not been enacted.`
obj_root_law_sections_15_footnotes:
  string
  line
